sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant D as Docusaurus core
    participant P as canonical-redirects plugin
    participant FS as outDir<br/>(emitted HTML)
    participant V as verifier

    Note over D,P: loadContent — pre-build
    D->>P: routesPaths
    P->>P: read scripts/redirects.json
    P->>P: validateRedirects (schema)
    P->>P: validateNoCycles
    P->>P: validateTargetsExist
    P->>P: buildRedirectMap() [once]

    Note over D,P: postBuild — post-emission
    D->>FS: emit HTML files
    P->>P: buildUniverse(routesPaths, CURRENT) [once]

    loop walk(outDir) — each .html
        P->>FS: read file
        P->>P: extractVersionInfo(rel)
        alt not version-prefixed
            P-->>P: skip (cloud/guides/templates/root)
        else version-prefixed
            P->>P: rewriteHtml(...)
            alt legacy version
                P->>P: canonical = self + inject noindex,follow meta
            else current / indexed version
                P->>P: resolveChain → rewrite canonical href
            else no canonical tag
                P-->>P: log.warn + counter
            end
            opt changed
                P->>FS: write file
            end
            P->>V: record canonical
        end
    end

    P->>V: verifyCanonicals(records, universe)
    loop each record
        alt legacy file
            V-->>P: skip (self-canonical trivially valid)
        else canonical ¬ startsWith(baseUrl)
            V-->>P: issue + fix hint
        else canonical path ∉ universe
            V-->>P: issue + fix hint
        end
    end

    P->>P: report summary
    alt issues && strict mode
        P-->>D: throw — fail build
    else
        P-->>D: done
    end
